HEADWORD: Amit
<hw>A*mit"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>amittere</ets>, <ets>amissum</ets>, to lose; <ets>a</ets>
(<ets>ab</ets>) + <ets>mittere</ets> to send. See
